[
  {
    "name": "section-hero",
    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: accessibility-hero-bg | Accessibility notice hero. Welcoming, inclusive imagery.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: welcoming dental office, accessible reception, inclusive care, accessibility at dentist.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x800, professional quality.\n       FALLBACK: Any welcoming, inclusive office photo.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero relative w-full min-h-[560px] md:min-h-[680px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.75), rgba(15,23,42,0.55), rgba(15,23,42,0.85)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=130');\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">Legal &amp; Compliance</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-title font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-6\">\n      Accessibility Notice\n    </h1>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-subtitle font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4\">\n      We are committed to ensuring digital and facility accessibility for people with disabilities. Every patient deserves seamless, barrier-free care and access to our services.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-description font-sans text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto text-[#3d5a6e]\">\n      We continually work to improve the user experience for everyone and apply relevant accessibility standards to ensure our website meets ADA compliance and WCAG 2.1 Level AA guidelines.\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-ada-commitment",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ada-commitment bg-white py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ada-commitment-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">Our Commitment</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ada-commitment-component-title font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-tight mb-6\">\n      ADA Compliance &amp; <span class=\"text-primary\">Accessibility Standards</span>\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ada-commitment-component-description text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 font-sans\">\n      Our practice is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We continually improve the user experience for everyone and apply relevant accessibility standards to our website and physical locations. We believe that all patients, regardless of ability, should have full access to the information and services we provide.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ada-commitment-component-standards-card bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 mb-8\">\n      <h3 class=\"font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-4\">Standards We Follow</h3>\n      <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\n        <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700 text-sm font-sans\">\n          <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"/></svg>\n          <span><strong class=\"text-gray-900 font-semibold\">WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong> - The internationally recognized benchmark for web accessibility, covering perceivable, operable, understandable, and robust content</span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700 text-sm font-sans\">\n          <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"/></svg>\n          <span><strong class=\"text-gray-900 font-semibold\">ADA Title III</strong> - The Americans with Disabilities Act requirements for public accommodations, ensuring equal access to goods and services</span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700 text-sm font-sans\">\n          <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"/></svg>\n          <span><strong class=\"text-gray-900 font-semibold\">Section 508</strong> - Federal standards for electronic and information technology accessibility</span>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-sans\">\n      Accessibility is an ongoing process, not a one-time project. We regularly review our website and physical spaces to identify and address potential barriers. Our team is trained to understand and respond to accessibility needs in both our digital presence and our office environment.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n      We recognize that accessibility requirements evolve as technology and best practices advance. Our practice stays informed about changes to accessibility guidelines and works proactively to incorporate improvements as they become available.\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-accessibility-features",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-[#f5f5f4]\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">What We've Implemented</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-title font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-tight mb-4\">\n      Accessibility <span class=\"text-primary\">Features</span>\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-description text-gray-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 font-sans\">\n      We have incorporated the following accessibility features throughout our website to ensure a barrier-free experience for all visitors, regardless of ability or the assistive technologies they use.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-black/[0.05]\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 17v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v6m-6 0h6m2 0H7\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-1-title font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-base mb-1\">Keyboard Navigation</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-1-description text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">All key areas of the site can be accessed and operated using a keyboard alone, without requiring a mouse or other pointing device.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-black/[0.05]\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"/><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-2-title font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-base mb-1\">Screen Reader Compatibility</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-2-description text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Our site is structured with proper semantic HTML, ARIA labels, and landmark regions to ensure compatibility with popular screen readers and assistive technologies.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-black/[0.05]\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-3-title font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-base mb-1\">Alternative Text for Images</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-3-description text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Descriptive alternative text is provided for all meaningful images so screen readers can convey visual content to users who are blind or have low vision.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-black/[0.05]\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-4-title font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-base mb-1\">Color Contrast</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-4-description text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">We maintain sufficient color contrast ratios between text and background elements to ensure readability for users with low vision or color vision deficiencies.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-black/[0.05]\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-5-title font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-base mb-1\">Form Labels and Instructions</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-5-description text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">All form fields include descriptive labels and clear instructions to ensure users can understand and complete forms without difficulty, including those using assistive technology.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-black/[0.05]\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0zM10 7v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0H7\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-6-title font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 text-base mb-1\">Resizable Text</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-accessibility-features-component-card-6-description text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Our website supports browser-based text resizing and zoom functionality, allowing users to adjust text size according to their individual preferences without loss of content or functionality.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-ongoing-efforts",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts bg-white py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">Continuous Improvement</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-title font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-tight mb-6\">\n      Ongoing <span class=\"text-primary\">Efforts</span>\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-description text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 font-sans\">\n      Accessibility is an ongoing commitment, not a single milestone. We continuously evaluate and improve our digital and physical environments to remove barriers and provide the best possible experience for all patients and visitors.\n    </p>\n\n    <div>\n\n      <div class=\"border-b border-gray-100 pb-8 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-block-1-title font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Regular Accessibility Audits</h3>\n        <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-block-1-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">We conduct periodic reviews of our website and facilities to identify accessibility issues and areas for improvement. These audits help us stay current with evolving standards and address new barriers as they arise. When issues are identified, we prioritize fixes based on their impact on users.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"border-b border-gray-100 pb-8 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-block-2-title font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Staff Training on Accessibility</h3>\n        <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-block-2-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">Our team members receive training on accessibility best practices, including how to assist patients with disabilities in our office and how to create accessible digital content. We believe that accessibility awareness should be part of every team member's professional development.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-block-3-title font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Third-Party Content Limitations</h3>\n        <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-ongoing-efforts-component-block-3-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">While we strive to make all content on our site accessible, some third-party tools or embedded content may not be fully accessible. We do not control these external vendors but encourage them to provide accessible experiences. We will continue to evaluate and update our third-party integrations as accessible alternatives become available.</p>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-feedback-contact",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-[#f5f5f4]\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">We're Here to Help</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-title font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-tight mb-6\">\n      Feedback &amp; <span class=\"text-primary\">Accessibility Support</span>\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-description text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 font-sans\">\n      If you experience any difficulty accessing any part of our website or need assistance with an in-office accommodation, we want to hear from you. Your feedback helps us improve the accessibility of our services for all patients.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-contact-card bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm mb-8\">\n\n      <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-6\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 8V5z\"/></svg>\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-phone text-gray-900 font-semibold text-base font-sans\">Phone</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm font-sans\">(555) 123-4567</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-6\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z\"/></svg>\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-email text-gray-900 font-semibold text-base font-sans\">Email</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm font-sans\">info@yourpractice.com</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\"/><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"/></svg>\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-feedback-contact-component-address text-gray-900 font-semibold text-base font-sans\">Mailing Address</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm font-sans\">123 Main Street, Suite 100<br>Your City, ST 12345</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n      We take all accessibility feedback seriously and will respond to your inquiry within two business days. If you need immediate assistance, please call our office during business hours and our team will be happy to help you.\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-cta",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta bg-primary py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans text-white/60\">Ready to Get Started</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-title font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white font-semibold leading-tight mb-5\">\n      Request an Appointment Today\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-description font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 text-white/90\">\n      Our team is here to provide personalized care in a welcoming, accessible environment. Schedule your visit today and experience the difference.\n    </p>\n\n\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n\n    <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-button inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-primary font-semibold py-4 px-10 rounded-full shadow-lg text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans\">\n      Request a Consultation\n      <svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3\"/></svg>\n    </a>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  }
]